parameters:
Hey, did you hear? There's a rumor about the test of that
scholarship student....

I heard, I heard. They say that that scholarship student got the
top score right after transferring schools? Wow... They really
are a genius, huh?

I heard that that scholarship student has been taking classes
that are already two years ahead since the first month. It seems
like the teachers' curriculum can't keep up...

They're on a completely different level from us, I can't help but
feel jealous. Maybe there has never been such a talented person
in the history of the school. Oh, by the way, what was the name
of the student who was in first place until then?

She's the young lady of the Lila family. Vega=Lila. That girl was
amazing at first too, you know.

They used to call her a child prodigy. But... I've witnessed a
true genius now...

In our school, if you're not the top student, you won't receive a
national pardon.... The declining Lila family might come to an
end with that child's generation. Hmph... serves them right.
My voice is so loud... What if someone hears me...

But, the Lila family is one of the top noble families, right? Is
it true that something serious is happening there?

Seriously. Like, seriously. I heard they failed in their mining
development, and there's a conflict happening nearby. It seems
like they can't focus on excavation work anymore.
...I mean, my dad lost his job and he was drinking heavily.

Well, I feel sorry for that girl too... I wonder what will happen
if her family disappears.

It's fine, really! Those nobles who are enjoying the sweet life
will get a taste of their own medicine. It's just the right
amount of pain!
That's why... I told you to speak louder...
